<mvc:View controllerName="dtt.SAPUI5.controller.HelloPanel" 
            xmlns="sap.m" 
            xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
            xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
            displayBlock="true">
    <Panel id="_IDGenPanel1" 
            headerText="{i18n>helloPanel}" 
            class="sapUIResponsiveMargin" 
            width="auto">
        <content>
            <Button id="_IDGenButt" 
                    text="{i18n>helloDialogButton}" 
                    press=".onOpenDialog" 
                    class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd" 
                    icon="sap-icon://action" />
            <Button id="_IDGenButton1" 
                    text="{i18n>showHelloButtonText}" 
                    press=".onShowHello" 
                    class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd" />
            <Input id="_IDGenInput1" 
                    value="{/recipient/name}" 
                    valueLiveUpdate="true" 
                    width="60%" />
            <Text id="_IDGenText1" 
                    text="hello{/recipient/name}" 
                    class="sapUiSmallMargin boldElements sapthemeHighlight-asColor" />
        </content>
    </Panel>
    <core:Fragment fragmentName="dtt.SAPUI5.view.Form01" 
                    type="XML" />
</mvc:View>
